com.amplifyframework.analytics

Class AnalyticsEvent.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.analytics.AnalyticsEvent.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    AnalyticsEvent

    public static final class AnalyticsEvent.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder is used to create and configure an instance of AnalyticsEvent. Its methods return the Builder instance to allow for fluent method chaining. This Builder reuses AnalyticsProperties.Builder to construct the properties to store in the event.
    See Also:
    AnalyticsProperties
